# pexip_infinity_ca_certificate (Resource)

Manages a CA certificate configuration with the Infinity service.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "pexip_infinity_ca_certificate" "example" {
  certificate = file("${path.module}/certificates/ca.crt")
}
```


